App & deployment part of the project created by github user @ed-roh
and published in form of an open github repository which is publicly available.
URL to the initial project: https://github.com/ed-roh/inventory-management/tree/master


The work presented in this project builds on top of the original ideas, expands them and upgrades with additions & modifications to the code base as long as with supplemental materials aiming at packaging the business use case for learning consumption